==English==

===Verb===
'''dole'''
# ''(dole out)'' To distribute in small amounts; to share out small portions of a meagre resource.

===Noun===
'''dole'''
# ''(British slang)'' payment by the state to the unemployed
#:''I get my '''dole''' paid twice a week.''
#:''I’ve been on the '''dole''' for two years now.''

